Class Summary
AllTests This test case aggregates all test cases.
Category Categories are used to classify components.

CompLink This class stores a link for the component version; e.g.
Component This class represents a component that can be application, assembly, testing or component.
CompUser This class represents an association between a component and a user, meaning that the user can view and change component data.
CompVersion This class represents a component's version.
CompVersionDates This class contains dates for each phase of a component version, as well as comments for those dates and some additional information.

StatusUserType This class introduced to store and to retrieve Status enumeration instances.
Technology This class represents a technology that a component version uses, like "XML", "EJB", "Spring" and so on.
TestHelper This is helper class containing certain widely used methods.
UnitTests This test case aggregates all Unit test cases.
 

Enum Summary
Status This class represents an enumeration of the possible status of a Component, a Category, a Technology or a CompVersionDates.
